      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.61,
      "size": 25776,
      "text": "有些最简单的式子，却能画出最复杂的图案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "henon-map",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "一条抛物线加一点点收缩，反复迭代，会发生什么？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "henon-map",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "答案是一片既杂乱又有序的点云，这就是埃农吸引子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "henon-map",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "埃农映射用两条公式把平面上的一点送到新位置。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "henon-map",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "define-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/define-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "新的横坐标是一减去 a 乘以 x 的平方，再加上 y。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "henon-map",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "define-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/define-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.72,
      "size": 43488,
      "text": "新的纵坐标则是 b 乘以旧的横坐标，经典取 a 等于一点四，b 等于零点三。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "henon-map",
      "section_id": "attractor",
      "line_id": "att-1",
      "filename": "attractor-att-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/attractor-att-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "从任意一点出发，前几步会四处游荡，这叫暂态。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "henon-map",
      "section_id": "attractor",
      "line_id": "att-2",
      "filename": "attractor-att-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/attractor-att-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.24,
      "size": 35856,
      "text": "丢掉暂态后，所有轨道都被吸进同一个形状里，无论从哪出发。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "henon-map",
      "section_id": "attractor",
      "line_id": "att-3",
      "filename": "attractor-att-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/attractor-att-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.36,
      "size": 21744,
      "text": "这个逃不出去的形状，就叫做吸引子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "henon-map",
      "section_id": "fractal",
      "line_id": "frac-1",
      "filename": "fractal-frac-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/fractal-frac-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "放大吸引子的任意一条曲线，会发现它其实由更多细线组成。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "henon-map",
      "section_id": "fractal",
      "line_id": "frac-2",
      "filename": "fractal-frac-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/fractal-frac-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "再放大，细线里还有细线，这种自我重复就是分形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "henon-map",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "调整参数 a，看吸引子如何被拉伸或折叠。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "henon-map",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "改变参数 b，观察点云从聚拢到散开的变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "henon-map",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "埃农映射用两条简单公式反复迭代平面上的点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "henon-map",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.36,
      "size": 21744,
      "text": "轨道收敛到一个自相似的分形吸引子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "henon-map",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/henon-map/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.83,
      "size": 29232,
      "text": "简单孕育复杂，这正是混沌之美，我们下次再见！"
